@startuml
!theme plain

title Diagramme de sequence - Planning infirmier

autonumber

actor Infirmier
boundary Frontend as "Application Angular"
control API as "Backend Spring Boot"
control ServicePlanning as "Service Planning"
database DB as "Base de donnees"

Infirmier -> Frontend: Consulter mon planning hebdomadaire
Frontend -> API: GET /planning/infirmiers/{id}?semaine=...
API -> ServicePlanning: chargerPlanning(id, semaine)
ServicePlanning -> DB: Lire affectations et shifts
DB --> ServicePlanning: Liste des shifts
ServicePlanning --> API: Planning formate
API --> Frontend: 200 OK + planning
Frontend --> Infirmier: Afficher planning

@enduml
